OL,3,CMan in court charged with bailiff's
OL,4,Cmurder
OL,6,FA man has appeared before a crown
OL,7,Fcourt judge after being charged with
OL,8,Fmurdering a bailiff at work.
OL,10,FFormer police officer Jeff Blair, 55,
OL,11,Fsuffered serious injuries and died
OL,12,Fafter an alleged attack in Shildon,
OL,13,FCounty Durham, on 10 March.
OL,15,FRobert Davies, 49, appeared at
OL,16,FTeesside Crown Court charged with his
OL,17,Fmurder, possession of an offensive
OL,18,Fweapon and affray.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/3
