PN,42302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1773756670
OL,3,CMan in court charged with bailiff's
OL,4,Cmurder
OL,6,FHe appeared at the hearing on Monday
OL,7,F(16 March) via a videolink from prison
OL,8,Ffor a hearing which lasted less than
OL,9,F10 minutes.
OL,11,FJudge Jonathan Carroll remanded him in
OL,12,Fcustody to appear before Leeds Crown
OL,13,FCourt for a plea hearing on 13 April.
OL,15,FMr Blair was a police officer with
OL,16,FDurham Constabulary for 22 years
OL,17,Fbefore retiring in 2017, prior to
OL,18,Fbecoming a court bailiff.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/3
