OL,3,CMan in court charged with bailiff's
OL,4,Cmurder
OL,6,FIn a statement, his family said: "Jeff
OL,7,Fwas a much-loved son, brother, father,
OL,8,Fpartner, uncle and good friend to many.
OL,10,F"His ability to apply humour and
OL,11,Flaughter to any situation and lighten
OL,12,Fthe mood will be irreplaceable to our
OL,13,Ffamily."
